\c 5
\s Imilayo elitshumi
\p
\v 1 UMozisi wasebiza uIsrayeli wonke, wathi kubo: Zwana, Israyeli, izimiso lezahlulelo engizikhuluma endlebeni zenu lamuhla, ukuze lizifunde, linanzelele ukuzenza.
\v 2 IN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wethu yenza isivumelwano lathi eHorebe\x + 4.23. Eks. 19.5.\x*.
\v 3 IN\nd kosi\nd* kayisenzanga lesisivumelwano labobaba, kodwa lathi, thina sonke esilapha siphila lamuhla\x + Heb. 8.9.\x*.
\v 4 IN\nd kosi\nd* yakhuluma lani ubuso lobuso entabeni, iphakathi komlilo\x + 34.10.\x*,
\v 5 (ngema phakathi kweN\nd kosi\nd* lani ngalesosikhathi, ukulazisa ilizwi leN\nd kosi\x + Eks. 20.21. Gal. 3.19.\x*\nd*; ngoba lesaba ngenxa yomlilo, kalenyukelanga entabeni)\x + Eks. 19.16. 20.18; 24.2.\x* isithi:
\p
\v 6 NgiyiN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wakho, eyakukhupha elizweni leGibhithe, endlini yobugqili\x + Eks.5.21. Eks. 20.2-17.\x*.
\p
\v 7 Ungabi labanye onkulunkulu phambi kwami.
\p
\v 8 Ungazenzeli isithombe esibaziweyo, loba yiwuphi umfanekiso wokusemazulwini phezulu loba wokusemhlabeni phansi, loba wokusemanzini ngaphansi komhlaba.
\v 9 Ungakukhothameli, ungakukhonzi; ngoba mina iN\nd kosi\nd*, uNkulunkulu wakho, nginguNkulunkulu olobukhwele, ngiphindisela ububi baboyise phezu kwabantwana, kuze kube se\add sizukulwane\add*ni sesithathu lesesine sabangizondayo,
\v 10 njalo ngibenzela umusa abayizinkulungwane zabangithandayo lezabagcina imilayo yami\x + Jer. 32.18. Dan. 9.4.\x*.
\p
\v 11 Ungaliphathi ngeze ibizo leN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wakho; ngoba iN\nd kosi\nd* kayiyikumyekela engelacala ophatha ibizo layo ngeze.
\p
\v 12 Gcina usuku lwesabatha, ukulungcwelisa, njengokukulaya kweN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wakho.
\v 13 Insuku eziyisithupha uzasebenza, uwenze wonke umsebenzi wakho;
\v 14 kodwa usuku lwesikhombisa lulisabatha leN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wakho; ungenzi loba yiwuphi umsebenzi \add ngalo\add*, wena lendodana yakho lendodakazi yakho lenceku yakho lencekukazi yakho lenkabi yakho lobabhemi wakho loba yisiphi sezifuyo zakho, lowemzini wakho ophakathi kwamasango akho, ukuze iphumule inceku yakho lencekukazi yakho, njengawe\x + Eks. 16.29,30. Heb. 4.4.\x*.
\v 15 Njalo ukhumbule ukuthi wawuyinceku elizweni leGibhithe\x + 15.15; 16.12; 24.18,22.\x*, lokuthi iN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wakho yakukhupha khona ngesandla esilamandla langengalo eyeluliweyo\x + 4.34,37.\x*. Ngakho iN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wakho yakulaya ukuthi ugcine usuku lwesabatha.
\p
\v 16 Hlonipha uyihlo lonyoko, njengokukulaya kweN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wakho, ukuze insuku zakho zelulwe, lokuthi kukulungele elizweni iN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wakho ekunika lona\x + 4.40.\x*.
\p
\v 17 Ungabulali\x + Luka 18.20. Jak. 2.11.\x*.
\p
\v 18 Njalo ungafebi\x + Luka 18.20. Jak. 2.11.\x*.
\p
\v 19 Njalo ungebi.
\p
\v 20 Njalo unganiki ubufakazi bamanga ngomakhelwane wakho.
\p
\v 21 Njalo ungafisi umkamakhelwane wakho; ungahawukeli indlu kamakhelwane wakho, insimu yakhe, lenceku yakhe, lencekukazi yakhe, inkabi yakhe, lobabhemi wakhe, njalo loba yini ekamakhelwane wakho.
\s Ukwesaba kwabantu
\p
\v 22 Amazwi la iN\nd kosi\nd* yawakhuluma ebandleni lenu lonke entabeni, iphakathi komlilo, eyezini, lemnyameni onzima, ngelizwi elikhulu; njalo kayengezelelanga. Yawabhala ezibhebheni ezimbili zamatshe, yanginika zona\x + Eks. 24.12.\x*.
\v 23 Kwasekusithi lilizwa ilizwi livela phakathi komnyama\x + 4.11.\x*, lentaba ivutha umlilo, lasondela kimi, zonke inhloko zezizwe zenu, labadala benu,
\v 24 lathi: Khangela, iN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wethu isitshengisile inkazimulo yayo lobukhulu bayo\x + 3.24; 11.2.\x*, lelizwi layo silizwile livela phakathi komlilo\x + Eks. 19.19.\x*; lamuhla sibonile ukuthi uNkulunkulu uyakhuluma lomuntu aphile\x + 4.33. Eks. 33.20.\x*.
\v 25 Ngakho-ke sizafelani? Ngoba lumlilo omkhulu uzasiqothula. Uba siphinda silizwa ilizwi leN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wethu futhi, sizakufa-ke\x + 18.16.\x*.
\v 26 Ngoba ngubani enyameni yonke owezwa ilizwi likaNkulunkulu ophilayo likhuluma livela phakathi komlilo, njengathi, waphila\x + 4.33.\x*?
\v 27 Sondela wena, uzwe konke iN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wethu ezakutsho, usitshele wena konke iN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wethu ezakutsho kuwe, sizakuzwa, sikwenze\x + Eks. 20.19.\x*.
\v 28 IN\nd kosi\nd* yasisizwa ilizwi lamazwi enu ekukhulumeni kwenu kimi; iN\nd kosi\nd* yasisithi kimi: Ngizwile ilizwi lamazwi alababantu abawakhulume kuwe; kulungile konke abakukhulumileyo\x + 18.17.\x*.
\v 29 O kungathi bangaba lenhliziyo enjalo yokungesaba, bagcine yonke imilayo yami, insuku zonke\x + 32.29. Hlab. 81.13. Isa. 48.18. Mat. 23.37. Luka 19.42.\x*, ukuze kubalungele labantwana babo kuze kube nininini\x + 4.40.\x*!
\v 30 Hamba uthi kibo: Zibuyeleleni emathenteni enu.
\v 31 Kodwa wena, mana lapha phansi kwami, ke ngikhulume kuwe yonke imilayo lezimiso lezahlulelo ozabafundisa zona, ukuze bazenze elizweni engibanika lona ukuthi badle ilifa lalo\x + Gal. 3.19.\x*.
\v 32 Ngakho qaphelani ukuthi lenze njengokulilaya kweN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wenu; lingaphambukeli ngakwesokunene langakwesokhohlo\x + 17.20; 28.14. Josh. 1.7; 23.6. Zaga 4.27.\x*.
\v 33 Lizahamba endleleni yonke iN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wenu elilaye yona, ukuze liphile\x + 10.12. 30.16. Jer. 7.23. Luka 1.6.\x*, njalo kulilungele, libe seliselula izinsuku elizweni elizakudla ilifa lalo\x + 4.40.\x*.
